    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_2",
      "block_index": 2,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "character_list",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "孙尚香：正旦",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 6,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_3",
      "block_index": 3,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "情节",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 2,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_4",
      "block_index": 4,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "赵云截江夺斗后，孙夫人独居江东。后关羽、张飞遇害，刘先主兴师大伐东吴，被陆逊用火攻之计，连营七百余里尽付一炬，先主仅以身免，赖赵云救往白帝城暂避。孙夫人在吴闻信，误谓先主已死，不胜悲痛，乃",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 94,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_5",
      "block_index": 5,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "请于国太，欲往江边祭奠，以尽夫妇之谊，国太允之。夫人至江边，易白衣冠望西号哭，竟投江而死。后人相传孙夫人投江后，上帝嘉其贞洁，封为枭姬。",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 68,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_6",
      "block_index": 6,
      "scene_id": null,
      "type": "plot_summary",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "根据《戏考》第二册整理",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 11,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_7",
      "block_index": 7,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "【第一场】",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_8",
      "block_index": 8,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "摆驾。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 3,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "内白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_9",
      "block_index": 9,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（四太监、四御林军、二宫女、孙尚香同上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 21,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_10",
      "block_index": 10,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "曾记得当年来辞君，棒打鸳鸯两离分。叹皇叔遭不幸龙归海境，不由奴日夜里珠泪淋淋。内侍臣摆驾江边来进，清风一去未亡人。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_16",
      "block_index": 16,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "祭礼摆下，着衣更换，两厢退下。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 15,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_17",
      "block_index": 17,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（四太监、四御林军同下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 13,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_18",
      "block_index": 18,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "设祭长江岸，举目望西川。梦魂何日见，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 18,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "念"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_19",
      "block_index": 19,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "夫君，先主！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "叫头"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_20",
      "block_index": 20,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "空自珠泪涟。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "念"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_21",
      "block_index": 21,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "孙尚香在江边心中酸疼，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "二黄导板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_22",
      "block_index": 22,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "夫君，先主！啊呀！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 9,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "三叫头"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_23",
      "block_index": 23,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "尊一声汉皇叔细听分明：",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "回龙"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_24",
      "block_index": 24,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "好夫妻恶姻缘悲哀告禀，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_25",
      "block_index": 25,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "凭空中便见听一点心诚。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_26",
      "block_index": 26,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你大英雄出身被困，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_27",
      "block_index": 27,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你结桃园义共死生；",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_28",
      "block_index": 28,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你破黄巾声名未重，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_29",
      "block_index": 29,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你虎牢关方显成名；",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_30",
      "block_index": 30,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你舍徐庶卧龙三请，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_31",
      "block_index": 31,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你水镜庄得一贤伦；",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_32",
      "block_index": 32,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你当阳道夏口夜奔，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_33",
      "block_index": 33,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你全仗着诸葛先生；",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_34",
      "block_index": 34,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你跳檀溪险些丧命，我的夫吓！",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 16,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_35",
      "block_index": 35,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（下锣。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_36",
      "block_index": 36,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "可叹你入虎穴东吴招亲。为报仇在猇亭遇见陆逊，又谁知那小贼果有才能。你不该七百里连营扎定，烧死了众儿郎百万雄兵。人报道你在白帝城丧命，那时节得凶信魂魄离身。实指望破奸曹狼烟扫尽，又谁知天不助命归天庭。我本当得此信寻个自尽，又恐怕我母亲不放离分。叹人生在世间如同照镜，夫已死我岂肯独自贪生。因此上备祭礼江边来进，但愿你魂灵儿早归天庭。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 11,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄慢板"
      ],
      "page_no": 1
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_51",
      "block_index": 51,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "且住。想皇叔一死，我在东吴苦守无益。不免拜谢母后养育之恩，投江自尽了吧。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 36,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_52",
      "block_index": 52,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "江水滔滔波浪滚，",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_53",
      "block_index": 53,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（四水旗同上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_54",
      "block_index": 54,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "aria",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "尚香拜别养育恩。辞别了老母后寻自尽，不如一死见夫君。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "唱",
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 8,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "反二黄摇板"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_57",
      "block_index": 57,
      "scene_id": "s_1",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（孙尚香、四水旗同下。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_58",
      "block_index": 58,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "scene_heading",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "【第二场】",
      "performance_tags": [],
      "char_len": 5,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_59",
      "block_index": 59,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（孙尚香上，四水旗引龙王同上。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 16,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_60",
      "block_index": 60,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_龙王",
      "text": "玉旨下，跪。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 6,
      "speaker_name_raw": "龙王",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_61",
      "block_index": 61,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "在。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 2,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_62",
      "block_index": 62,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_龙王",
      "text": "听宣读。诏曰：孙尚香为夫投江，尽节一死，玉帝垂怜，封为枭姬娘娘。旨意读罢，望诏谢恩。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 42,
      "speaker_name_raw": "龙王",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_63",
      "block_index": 63,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker_id": "c_孙尚香",
      "text": "圣寿无疆。",
      "performance_tags": [
        "念"
      ],
      "char_len": 5,
      "speaker_name_raw": "孙尚香",
      "performance_cues_raw": [
        "白"
      ],
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_64",
      "block_index": 64,
      "scene_id": "s_2",
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "speaker_id": null,
      "text": "（龙王下。孙尚香换衣。）",
      "performance_tags": [
        "做"
      ],
      "char_len": 12,
      "page_no": 2
    },
    {
      "block_id": "b_65",
      "block_index": 65,
